{"tid":1490540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Twitter 戰線] 建立連登群體！有效傳播資訊！","createTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:08:35.000Z","uid":212944,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"fcb578d0b2c0a843c6f73883612f07d1562c089d","tid":1490540,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:19.000Z","msg":"小妹之前一路都係用twitter來follow 外國明星 同埋youtuber，比較似個CD-rom ，唔係點出post，係由反送中運動開始先用twitter來推外國文宣。<br />\n<br />\n經過琴日太柒地集體洗版，我發現問題源於香港人Local係twitter嘅community太細，以致有好多post都只係清一色hashtag，無乜特別content，而亦都因為我地個Community太細，令到我地無太多followers，以致更加難推Post。<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我希望大家可以係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 所有post都加返 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">#HongKong #HongKongProtest</span></strong>. 而家有好多 #HongKong 嘅post都係CCTV , 人民日報 同環球時報呢D黨媒<br />\n2. 禁入去 #HongKong #HongKongProtest 之後，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">試下揾同路人acc，然後互相follow</span></strong>。 我地要自己建立一個群體先。呢個時候，我地可以 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#LIHKG #LIHKGJAI</span></span></strong>，再用呢個hashtag來follow同路人<br />\n3. 之後我地要target 3個方向<br />\n1) #Chinazi ： 主力打中國點獨裁納粹、親中嘅點對待百姓、佢地會講hate speech (曱甴)<br />\n2) #Feminism, #metoo, #Sexualassault ：講警方使用嘅性暴力，例如搞到女仔走光、男仔搜女仔、今日警棍插伯伯下體同肛門(形同雞姦)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3) #Policebrutality #HKpolice #BoycottMulan ：講警方點濫暴，記得最後要反問句 &quot;Is this what Mulan Actress Liu Yi-fei supports?&quot; <br />\n<br />\n小妹之前都有個post係講一D用twitter嘅意見，歡迎大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我地一定要將黑警上升到國際話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1489932/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1489932/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eced70607de495ec6c761048788dc0253e2f60d","tid":1490540,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:46:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0635562333cece97cb10a7807a509c6bf5842c78","tid":1490540,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"76740d39044f0c161efde2ddbf27311e3fe5d57e","tid":1490540,"uid":212944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"Twitter #LIHKG #LIHKGJAI"},{"pid":"a731706a4a0c00c3816053eed1cdd2836401bf0b","tid":1490540,"uid":217413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n快速入門，教你如何用Twitter<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489008</a>"},{"pid":"ba29d9dcf771d1ba31b37aed6e8cd8e8ebf77979","tid":1490540,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c6847d43e20e389bfc02a40a787938d84d09d05","tid":1490540,"uid":212944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n建議所有Twitter #LIHKG #LIHKGJAI，然後互相follow 互相retweet!!!"},{"pid":"673d3999e7fc571e362b59307055d6f3faa8aef9","tid":1490540,"uid":212944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線嘅同我入來！！少少意見！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1489932/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1489932/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"bccc8ca4f32699fd1af332f454168ecf74e43d11","tid":1490540,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25bff304182eb0ed28